<div id="content">
							<h1 class="arc-post-title">Uncategorized</h1><h3 class="arc-src">now browsing by category</h3>
				<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>
		
				
			<div class="post-228 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
				<p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on October 17, 2012</p>
                <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=228">Breaking News</a></h2>
				<div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>	
				<div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-13" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/news-title1.png" alt="" width="349" height="104" /></a></p>
<p><strong>Breaking News Report!!!</strong></p>
<p>Our field reporters on the outskirts of the Eko Eko Desert are reporting some very strange events and suspicious activity. We have asked them to stay in the field to continue sending us back their reports.</p>
<p>We are asking ALL witnesses to ANY strange behavior – managers disappearing or Ekos turning into ghosts or sightings of other strange creatures – to PLEASE contact us at <a href="mailto:usa_blog@ekoloko.com">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</a> with your eye-witness reports!!!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p>And here’s some more breaking news: The design contest is OVER – thanks to everyone for their great submissions!</p>
<p><strong>We have our winners</strong>!!!</p>
<p>Congratulations to Blueking1:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-a.png" ><img class="wp-image-232 alignnone" title="Blueking1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-a.png" alt="" width="347" height="197" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations to Mazaii-Avrila-Taleko:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-c.png" ><img class="wp-image-234 alignnone" title="Mazaii_Avrila_Taleko" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-c.png" alt="" width="367" height="174" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations to Dancing4lyfe:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-e.jpg" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-236" title="Dancing" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-e.jpg" alt="" width="288" height="216" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations to AvimarS:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-d.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-235" title="AvimarS" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-d.png" alt="" width="347" height="197" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations to Butterfly:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-f.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-231" title="Butterfly" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-f.png" alt="" width="347" height="197" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations to FastTime:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-b.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-230" title="FastTime" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-b.png" alt="" width="347" height="197" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations to YuvalXD:</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-g.png" ><img class="alignnone  wp-image-233" title="YuvalXD" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/winner-g.png" alt="" width="347" height="197" /></a></p>
<p>Each of our lucky winners has been awarded 300 Kokos!!! (<span style="color: #00ccff;">If you were part of a group, the prize is shared</span>.)</p>
<p><strong>New contest next week!!!!!!</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
				</div>
